        The application id.

      • clientKey

        public String clientKey
        The client key.

      • apiTimeout

        public int apiTimeout
        The time out of most api request. By default, the value is 15000 MILLISECONDS.

      • retryTimes

        public int retryTimes
        The retry times of most api request.By default, the value is 4 times.

      • analyticsEnable

        public boolean analyticsEnable
        Whether the Analytics service is enable or not. Default is true.

      • autoTrackStrategy

        public int autoTrackStrategy
        Whether the Session and PageView auto tracking is enable or not. Default is disable. Auto tracking only works on level 14 or higher.

      • sessionContinueTime

        public long sessionContinueTime
        The duration each session has. Default value is 30*1000 MILLISECONDS.

      • marketingEnable

        public boolean marketingEnable
        Whether the Marketing service is enable or not. Default is false.

      • refreshConfigWhenAppCreated

        public boolean refreshConfigWhenAppCreated
        Whether the CloudConfig is refreshed when open app. Default is true.

      • analyticsCollectionStrategy

        public AnalyticsCollectionStrategy analyticsCollectionStrategy
        The strategy of collect Analytics information. Default is collect at once.

      • serverRegion

        public String serverRegion
        The server region. Default is US.

      • enableAnonymousUser

        public boolean enableAnonymousUser
        The AnonymousUser defult true.
